          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A pixel buffer adaptor provides a pixel buffer pool that you use to allocate pixel buffers to the output file. Using the provided pool for buffer allocation is typically more efficient than managing your own pool."
